			I play Japanese mahjong (Riichi) a lot. The best way to get into it is watching <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Akagi_%28manga%29">Akagi</a>, a dark and intense anime about mahjong. Another great anime about bizarre high stakes gambling is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kaiji_%28manga%29">Kaiji</a>. Mahjong games can get <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=neFgMfwqN-c">very intense</a>.
